MagicWord
-----------------------------------------------

1) Configure authentication as found in the Django documentation (http://www.djangoproject.com/documentation/authentication/).

2) Add magicword to INSTALLED_APPS in settings.py.

3) Add the following to settings.py:

AUTHENTICATION_BACKENDS = (
    'magicword.magicauth.MagicBackend',
    'django.contrib.auth.backends.ModelBackend',
)

4) Replace the username field in registration/login.html (or a custom login form) with a hidden username field with a value of 'guest'.